description: Demolition of buildings and redevelopment FOR mixed use totalling 83,915m (GEA) comprising 286 flats (C3), 25,769m  office floorspace (B1), 1,170m  of retail floorspace (A), 562m  of  D1 (community) uses, new open space, reconfigured vehicular and pedestrian access and works to the public highway with associated works including landscaping and basement car park for 82 cars, plus  servicing and plant areas. The development consists of two towers: an office tower of 23 storeys (maximum height 105m Above Ordinance Datum), a residential tower of 42 storeys (maximum height 148m AOD) and lower rise buildings of up to 7 storeys fronting Stamford Street and Paris Gardens.
